{{!
    @template format_tiles/filterbutton

    Flter button template.

    The purpose of this template is to render a singe filter button
    which the user can click to filter down which course tiles are being
    displayed

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
        * id - id number of the filter button
        * buttonnum - sequence number of the button
        * sections - which sections it relate to when pressed
        * title - what to display on the button

    Example context (json):
    {
        "id": 12345,
        "buttonnum": 2,
        "sections": [3,4,5],
        "title": "3-5"
        }
}}

<div id="{{id}}" class="filterbutton" data-buttonid="{{buttonnum}}" data-sections="{{sections}}">
  {{{title}}}
</div>